{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":null,"text":"他终于长成了！","tone":"欣慰","chapter":58,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":null,"text":"我们也该回家了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":8,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_leng_han_zhu","speaker_name":"冷寒竹","listener":"char_leng_ku_mu","text":"赌约呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":58,"line_start":10,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_leng_ku_mu","speaker_name":"冷枯木","listener":null,"text":"什么赌约，胜负负，还有什么关系么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":12,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_zhan_fei","speaker_name":"战飞","listener":null,"text":"人生，人生……唉！去了……去了！","tone":"无奈","chapter":58,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_bian_shao_yan","speaker_name":"边少衍","listener":null,"text":"檀明跑了，我们怎么办？","tone":"焦急","chapter":58,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_liu_hui","speaker_name":"柳辉","listener":null,"text":"他跑得掉么？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":58,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_gong_qing_yang","speaker_name":"龚清洋","listener":null,"text":"他自认杀死‘枪剑无敌’，裴玺怎会放过他，迟早是死路一条！","tone":"冷笑","chapter":58,"line_start":48,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_liu_hui","speaker_name":"柳辉","listener":null,"text":"只要檀明一死，哈哈……‘飞龙镖局’的账薄、存折、营业情况，全都捏在我手里，我们三人可真要扬眉吐气了。","tone":"大笑","chapter":58,"line_start":52,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_gong_qing_yang","speaker_name":"龚清洋","listener":null,"text":"何况我们这番已与‘江南同盟’拉上了交情，改组后的‘飞龙镖局’，将来想必是一片坦途了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":58,"line_start":58,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_liu_hui","speaker_name":"柳辉","listener":"char_gong_qing_yang","text":"龚兄，将来‘飞龙镖局’的总镖头位子，想来要归于龚兄的了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":58,"line_start":64,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_gong_qing_yang","speaker_name":"龚清洋","listener":null,"text":"柳兄说哪里话？总镖头一位，自然是柳兄的了！","tone":"苦笑","chapter":58,"line_start":68,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_bian_shao_yan","speaker_name":"边少衍","listener":null,"text":"柳总镖头，将来‘飞龙镖局’还有小弟容身之地么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":58,"line_start":74,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_liu_hui","speaker_name":"柳辉","listener":"char_bian_shao_yan","text":"边兄，说哪里话？无论以声名截或武功来说，将来‘飞龙镖局’的总镖头一位，却该是边兄的。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":58,"line_start":78,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_bian_shao_yan","speaker_name":"边少衍","listener":null,"text":"如此说来……","tone":"大笑","chapter":58,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_liu_hui","speaker_name":"柳辉","listener":"char_miao_bao","text":"谁！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":58,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_miao_bao","speaker_name":"苒豹","listener":null,"text":"两位打得好如意的算盘！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":58,"line_start":92,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_liu_hui","speaker_name":"柳辉","listener":"char_miao_bao","text":"豹兄，你……你怎地来了？","tone":"恐惧","chapter":58,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_miao_bao","speaker_name":"苒豹","listener":null,"text":"你连檀大爷都不认得了，还认得我吗？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":58,"line_start":98,"line_end":98},{"speaker":"char_liu_hui","speaker_name":"柳辉","listener":null,"text":"我……我……","tone":"恐惧","chapter":58,"line_start":100,"line_end":100}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_yuan_lu_zhen","name":"袁泸珍","alias":[],"identity":"武林人士","faction":"江南同盟","role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"对裴玺忠心聋聋的同伴","personality":{"traits":["忠诚","热心","善良","正直","重情义"],"speech_style":"直率","temperament":"热忕"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":58,"line_start":4,"line_end":4,"text":"袁泸珍热泪盈眶"}]},{"id":"char_leng_han_zhu","name":"冷寒竹","alias":["冷谷双木"],"identity":"冷谷双木之一","faction":"冷谷","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"冷谷双木中的兄长","personality":{"traits":["冷峻","深沉","高傲","内敛","智慧"],"speech_style":"简洁","temperament":"冷静"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":58,"line_start":6,"line_end":6,"text":"冷寒竹道"}]},{"id":"char_leng_ku_mu","name":"冷枯木","alias":["冷谷双木"],"ident